OL,3,CWealth of Rishi Sunak and wife jumps
OL,4,Cmore than #120 million to #651 million
OL,6,FThe personal fortune of the and his
OL,7,Fwife Akshata Murty has surged by more
OL,8,Fthan #120 million over the past year,
OL,9,Fbringing their total wealth to #651
OL,10,Fmillion.
OL,12,FThe latest annual Sunday Times Rich
OL,13,FList revealed their wealth grew
OL,14,Fsubstantially despite the wider UK
OL,15,Fbillionaire boom coming "to an end" in
OL,16,Fthe face of tough economic conditions.
OL,18,Fwealth has grown more than #120
OL,19,Fmillion in the last year, soaring from
OL,20,F#529 million in 2023.
