OL,3,CWealth of Rishi Sunak and wife jumps
OL,4,Cmore than #120 million to #651 million
OL,6,FThe rise was linked to Ms Murty's
OL,7,Fsmall stake in Infosys, the $70
OL,8,Fbillion (#55.3 billion) Indian IT
OL,9,Fgiant co-founded by her billionaire
OL,10,Ffather.
OL,12,FHer shares grew in value by #108.8
OL,13,Fmillion to nearly #590 million for the
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,FThe couple's wealth however still
OL,17,Fremains below its level from 2022,
OL,18,Fwhen it sat at around #730 million for
OL,19,Fthe year.
