OL,3,CWealth of Rishi Sunak and wife jumps
OL,4,Cmore than #120 million to #651 million
OL,6,FThe number of billionaires reached a
OL,7,Fpeak of 177 in 2022, before dropping
OL,8,Fto 171 and falling again to 165 this
OL,9,Fyear, driven by some seeing their
OL,10,Fprivate wealth contract amid high
OL,11,Fborrowing rates and others leaving the
OL,12,Fcountry.
OL,14,FRobert Watts, compiler of the rich
OL,15,Flist, said it suggests Britain's
OL,16,Fbillionaire boom has come to an end.
OL,18,F"Many of our home-grown entrepreneurs
OL,19,Fhave seen their fortunes fall and some
OL,20,Fof the global super rich who came here
OL,21,Fare moving away.
