OL,6,F"Thousands of British livelihoods rely
OL,7,Fon the super-rich to some extent.
OL,9,F"We'll have to wait and see whether we
OL,10,Fhave now reached peak billionaire, and
OL,11,Fwhat that means for our economy."
OL,13,FThe list of Britain's 350 wealthiest
OL,14,Findividuals and families together hold
OL,15,Fcombined wealth of #795.36 billion,
OL,16,Faccording to the new data.
OL,18,FThis year's list was once again topped
OL,19,Fby Gopi Hinduja and his family, who
OL,20,Fcontrol the Indian conglomerate
OL,21,FHinduja Group.
