OL,3,CWealth of Rishi Sunak and wife jumps
OL,4,Cmore than #120 million to #651 million
OL,6,FMr Hinduja and his family saw their
OL,7,Fwealth rise to #37.2 billion for the
OL,8,Fyear from #35 billion.
OL,10,FMeanwhile, a number of the UK's
OL,11,Fhighest profile billionaires saw their
OL,12,Ffortunes shrink over the year amid
OL,13,Fchallenging periods for many
OL,14,Fbusinesses and investments.
OL,16,FSir Jim Ratcliffe, Sir James Dyson and
OL,17,FSir Richard Branson also recorded
OL,18,Fdeclines for the year.
